metadata.name: Shamyreen Towlagh
metadata.description:
Shamyreen Towlagh is Manx Gaelic for ‘Manifold’.

The mind is a labyrinthine realm. It is it’s own unending space-time, folded in upon itself; and folded inward again and again. 

We wander its living surfaces. We explore our deepest selves. What will we find here? What secrets? What power?

Artist: Matt Brown
